{
  "stem": "25027.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To protect the general population-- I would say the Jewish population-- from pogroms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember a Ukrainian peasant came into the middle of the city, riding a officer-- Polish officer's horse, and he was dragging the Polish officers behind him-- all tied up and beaten to a pulp.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they hated each other-- the Poles and the Ukrainians never got along.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Poles were as bad to the Ukrainians as they were to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Ukrainians were as bad to the Jews as the Poles were to the Jews-- exactly what's going on in Croatia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the Muslims are fighting the Catholics, the Catholics are fighting the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not the Protestants, the Pravoslavnis, which is Russian Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had the same situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Positively.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they picked up some guns-- I don't know where the guns came from-- rifles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a militia right away, a local militia, which was this barge right after the Russians came, within a day or so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did have local Communists who-- Jewish Communists-- who became the rulers of the town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They worked in cahoots with the Russian-- new Russian military government that came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They eliminated private stores-- the well-to-do Jews, their stores were confiscated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Many of them, apparently, when known that they were anti-Communists, were sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened to them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Religion was frowned upon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like I said, they had Yiddish in the schools, but not religion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They started closing some of the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We received a passport-- a Russian Soviet passport-- saying that we are Soviet citizen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it said we're [RUSSIAN], which means Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
